author: Asa Bennett
title: Can you recognise Labour's Brexit rebels?
text:
L abour unity has collapsed over Brexit as 17 frontbenchers defied Jeremy Corbynâ€™s wishes by voted against legislation to trigger leaving the EU .
Four of them quit before the vote, so the Labour leader will be thinking a lot about whether he has to punish the 13 rebels who haven't done so yet, as sacking them would force him to carry out his third reshuffle in 18 months.
Watch | How Article 50 will divide the Labour party 01:44 G iven how fast he is going through new shadow ministers, we decided to mark this recent rebellion by rounding up 10 of Labour's frontbench rebels to see if you can tell who they are in our special Article 50 quiz.
